trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of media related commands.
trans-unit.target: 표준 제공 미디어 세트 관련 명령입니다.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the MediaCommands class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: MediaCommands 클래스에서 명령 및의 다른 명령을 라이브러리 클래스와 같은 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands>및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>, 응용 프로그램 프로그래머는 자주 발생 하는 일반적인 명령 집합을 나타내는 하기 위한 것입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands>

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: 명령을 나타낼의 인스턴스는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>및 명령에 대 한 구현 논리 아닙니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 에 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A> 를 통해 구현 논리와 명령에 연결이 바인딩됩니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic which performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer will be responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target will handle the command.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어 경우는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A>컨트롤 (명령 대상)을 수행 하는 논리에서 명령이 실행 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A>명령 명령 대상 응용 프로그램 개발자는 기울여야 명령 대상이 명령을 처리 하는 방법을 결정 하는 논리를 작성 해야 하는 제공 되지 않을 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.MediaCommands.Play%2A>

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: 여러 컨트롤의 많은 명령 라이브러리의 명령에 대 한 구현 논리를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>클래스에 대 한 논리를 제공는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>명령을 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>명령을 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>명령을 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>명령 및 <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A>명령입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding see the [Commanding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 명령 및 명령 실행에 대 한 자세한 내용은 [명령 실행 개요](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)합니다.
